Interface StorageConfigurationTags

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ConfigurationTags

    public interface StorageConfigurationTags
extends ConfigurationTags
    A collection of tags for configuration files. These occur in the XML configuration file and are used by providers to get the associated values.
